snippet.title: Operation Amber Sky | Ghost Recon Breakpoint R6 Siege Crossover Event LEAKED
snippet.description:
Mark your calendars Ghosts! Operation Amber Sky is the new Crossover event in Ghost Recon Breakpoint that will feature Rainbow Six Siege characters and this event is going live on January 21st! This is really exciting considering how slowly the Breakpoint updates have been rolling out lately and I can't wait to jump back into Breakpoint to check out this new content.
00:00 Intro
02:32 Open World PVP Idea
03:04 Wildlands 2 Idea

Here is my open world PVP idea as mentioned in the video: https://youtu.be/czkFlkh2GRE

Here is my community inspired idea for a Wildlands 2: https://youtu.be/Y-7uQpfRTgg
